data.description: **Seller contribution or credit available** 2001 single-family home in St. James Golf Club, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This well-maintained residence boasts an updated master shower, offering comfort and style. Enjoy the serene atmosphere with a backyard overlooking the lush golf course, providing stunning views and a peaceful retreat. Located in a gated community, the HOA includes access to a pool, playground, basketball courts, tennis courts, pickball, fitness center, lawn services, basic cable tv, and high speed internet. This home offers the perfect blend of contemporary living, classic charm, and an array of recreational amenities. Schedule a tour today!
